title: Fitbit Local San Diego Tickets, Sun, Oct 16, 2016 at 9:00 AM | Eventbrite
text:
Event description Description 
Sweat it out with Fitbit Local, a series of free monthly workouts in your city, led by fitness leaders from your community.Crush your step count on a gorgeous fall morning with Fitbit Local Ambassadors Sheri Matthews & Mike Sherbakov. Join us Sunday morning at Torrey Pines State Reserve at the bottom of the hill on the north side (near the parking lot benches). Bring a friend (or six!), and enter for a chance to win a Fitbit tracker. Looking for even more motivation? Join Step It Up: a nationwide challenge to walk as much as possible from October 13-26. Create a team or sign up solo, compete in daily face-offs and commit to moving more.
